小熊一般會跟在母親身邊長達2年半、甚至3年、感情親密。在此过程中小熊會逐渐斷奶，開始食用母親獵捕到的食物，並跟著母親學習各種在未來獨立後、賴以生存的狩獵技能<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3126440/Polar-bear-mother-teaches-young-hunt-patiently-waiting-seals-breathing-hole-ruthlessly-snatching-one-dinner.html|title=Polar bear teaches young to hunt seals by waiting near breathing hole|publisher=|accessdate=2016-08-30|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011013325/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3126440/Polar-bear-mother-teaches-young-hunt-patiently-waiting-seals-breathing-hole-ruthlessly-snatching-one-dinner.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

小北極熊最大的天敵是成年的公熊，有記錄公熊追殺小熊、甚至少數有吃食的情形，因此有小熊的母親，都會儘量避開公熊<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=No70mI2lJD8.|Uploaded on Nov 4, 2007
National Geographic Polar Bear Mom protects cubs
Canada's frozen north in the Tundra Buggy Lodge</ref>，但在必要時、僅管體型可能只有公熊的一半，母熊仍會努力捍衛小熊<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XbyxI-d5idcC&pg=PA84&lpg=PA84&dq=polar%20bear%20cub%20hunting%20skills&source=bl&ots=oiC-ZITZ7A&sig=7anhp7y26K3FTwMbTD0F4t2muqQ&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwic8pex8OfOAhVNwWMKHZQLBwgQ6AEIXjAL#v=onepage&q=polar%20bear%20cub%20hunting%20skills&f=false|title=An Introduction to Marine Mammal Biology and Conswervation|first1=Parsons|last1=ECM|first2=Bauer|last2=A|first3=Simmonds|last3=M.P|first4=Wright|last4=A.J|first5=McCafferty|last5=D|date=2012-04-11|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|via=Google Books}}</ref><ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nQHbZ9UYovs.|Published on Jun 13, 2012
Brad Josephs filmed this amazing clip in Alaska of a Polar Bear mother protecting defending her cubs from male Polar Bear</ref>。

由於小北極熊在三歲前狩獵的經驗不足，幾乎仰賴母親的乳汁、或獵捕、找到的食物生存，當母親的食物來源不夠時，本身的乳汁也會枯竭<ref>Polar Bear : A Complete Guide to their Biology and Behavior, page 187</ref>，以致小熊餓死，因此一般而言，只有經驗豐富、擅於捕獵的母親、才能夠讓小熊在北極嚴酷的環境中生存下來<ref>Polar Bear : A Complete Guide to their Biology and Behavior, page 179</ref>。

