一般人可能認為北極熊捕食海豹輕而易舉，事實上，在穩固又適宜的[[海冰|海冰]]、或冰間湖上，北極熊獵捕五六次的成功機率，可能只有一次<ref>Polar Bear : A Complete Guide to their Biology and Behaviour, page 130</ref>。而在開放海域上的[[海冰|海冰]]，獵捕成功的機率會降到佰分之五以下。每二十次的獵捕，可能只有一次會成功。<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Nrr7nZVdQQ.|Brilliant wildlife video from BBC nature show 'Animals: The Inside Story'. Learn how a pregnant polar bear survivies in the gruelling winter months.</ref><ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0mgnf6t9VEc.|As the sea ice begins to break up in Summer, a polar bear ingeniously uses the drift ice to sneak up on a seal. Published on Nov 4, 2015 by BBC, Programme website: http://bbc.in/1iD3ju5</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polarresearch.net/index.php/polar/article/viewFile/6921/7754|title=Polar Research: Vol 36, No 1|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920184223/http://www.polarresearch.net/index.php/polar/article/viewFile/6921/7754|archive-date=2016-09-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在海中海豹遠較北極熊靈活、下潛速度快，此外北極熊無法閉氣過久（一般是一分多鐘，而海豹可達40幾分鐘）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npolar.no/en/species/ringed-seal.html|title=Ringed seal (Pusa hispida)|publisher=|accessdate=2016-08-30|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919204548/http://www.npolar.no/en/species/ringed-seal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此北極熊幾乎無法在海中追捕到海豹。在開放海域上的[[海冰|海冰]]，海豹極容易潛入海水逃脫，導致北極熊成功獵捕的機會很低。

